{"tid":2440884,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"測量員認藏剪鉗　還柙候判　鄭念慈:打算判監","createTime":"2021-03-10T09:27:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T11:41:21.000Z","uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d660160ad26f4c16a21f98c7b6995637def357d0","tid":2440884,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T09:27:44.000Z","msg":"2019 年 11 月接連發生「三罷」、理大被警方圍堵，多區爆發警民衝突。26 歲測量員被指在地鐵站路軌明渠中藏有剪鉗，被控「管有適合作非法用途的工具並意圖作非法用途使用」。被告今（10 日）於九龍城裁判法院認罪，裁判官鄭念慈指，會先索取社會服務令報告，案件押後至本月 24 日判刑，惟鄭明言打算判監，被告期間須還柙。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官在聽取求情時，一度打斷謂「冇諗住用咁拎嚟做咩？」「不時之需即係咩呀？」，又質疑該路軌範圍是獲授權人士才可進入，被告管有剪鉗「可以破壞一啲設施嫁喎」。辯方強調，沒有證據證明被告有進行破壞，裁判官則指，「破壞咗就唔係呢個控罪啦」。"},{"pid":"6c5b3f2b7b8264b91fd0f5e18f94d9cd05a62033","tid":2440884,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T09:27:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E6%B8%AC%E9%87%8F%E5%93%A1%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%98%8E%E6%B8%A0%E4%B8%AD%E8%97%8F%E5%89%AA%E9%89%97-%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA%E9%82%84%E6%9F%99%E5%80%99%E5%88%A4-%E8%A3%81%E5%88%A4%E5%AE%98%E6%98%8E%E8%A8%80%E6%89%93%E7%AE%97%E5%88%A4%E7%9B%A3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E9%2587%258F%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2598%258E%25E6%25B8%25A0%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%2597%258F%25E5%2589%25AA%25E9%2589%2597-%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E9%2582%2584%25E6%259F%2599%25E5%2580%2599%25E5%2588%25A4-%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2598%258E%25E8%25A8%2580%25E6%2589%2593%25E7%25AE%2597%25E5%2588%25A4%25E7%259B%25A3%2F&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplUuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=07a1768d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E9%2587%258F%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%2598%258E